quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  72,20,dictus ego worship unus my Dominus; ego nunquam set any idols Eum
  72,21,dictus ego non possess power harm vos nor guide vos
  72,22,dictus Non 1 protect me DEUS nor potuit ego invenit any alius refuge Eum
  72,23,Ego deliver deus proclamations messages Those disobey DEUS His messenger incur fire Hell wherein they abide forever
  72,24,Dodum they vide quod awaiting them they perfecit invenit out qui est really infirmus in power fewer in numerus
  72,25,dictus ego non know quod promised vos happen soon alias my Dominus delay it pro awhile
  72,26,He est Knower future He non reveal future anyone
  72,27,Unus to messenger He chooses perfecit He reveal preter future specific news
  72,28,Hoc est ascertain ut they delivered their Dominus messages He est fully aware de quod they habet. He comes numerus totus things